{
  "video_id": "qpfq3xCdAu4",
  "title": "How fungi recognize (and infect) plants | Mennat El Ghalid",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12825.0,
      "end_time": 15514.0,
      "text": "\"Will the blight end the chestnut?"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15857.0,
      "end_time": 17857.0,
      "text": "The farmers rather guess not."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 17881.0,
      "end_time": 20119.0,
      "text": "It keeps smouldering at the roots"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 20143.0,
      "end_time": 22151.0,
      "text": "And sending up new shoots"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 22175.0,
      "end_time": 23841.0,
      "text": "Till another parasite"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 23865.0,
      "end_time": 26269.0,
      "text": "Shall come to end the blight.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 28510.0,
      "end_time": 30549.0,
      "text": "At the beginning of the 20th century,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 30573.0,
      "end_time": 35220.0,
      "text": "the eastern American chestnut population, counting nearly four billion trees,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 35244.0,
      "end_time": 38345.0,
      "text": "was completely decimated by a fungal infection."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 38369.0,
      "end_time": 41577.0,
      "text": "Fungi are the most destructive pathogens of plants,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 41601.0,
      "end_time": 44323.0,
      "text": "including crops of major economic importance."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 44673.0,
      "end_time": 46234.0,
      "text": "Can you imagine that today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 46258.0,
      "end_time": 49125.0,
      "text": "crop losses associated with fungal infection"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 49149.0,
      "end_time": 53650.0,
      "text": "are estimated at billions of dollars per year, worldwide?"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 53585.0,
      "end_time": 57283.0,
      "text": "That represents enough food calories to feed half a billion people."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 57609.0,
      "end_time": 59967.0,
      "text": "And this leads to severe repercussions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 59991.0,
      "end_time": 63411.0,
      "text": "including episodes of famine in developing countries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 63435.0,
      "end_time": 66839.0,
      "text": "large reduction of income for farmers and distributors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 66863.0,
      "end_time": 68791.0,
      "text": "high prices for consumers"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 68815.0,
      "end_time": 73539.0,
      "text": "and risk of exposure to mycotoxin, poison produced by fungi."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 74318.0,
      "end_time": 75580.0,
      "text": "The problems that we face"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 75604.0,
      "end_time": 78321.0,
      "text": "is that the current method used to prevent and treat"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 78345.0,
      "end_time": 79887.0,
      "text": "those dreadful diseases,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 79911.0,
      "end_time": 84220.0,
      "text": "such as genetic control, exploiting natural sources of resistance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 84244.0,
      "end_time": 87625.0,
      "text": "crop rotation or seed treatment, among others,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 87649.0,
      "end_time": 90331.0,
      "text": "are still limited or ephemeral."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 90879.0,
      "end_time": 93299.0,
      "text": "They have to be constantly renewed."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 93323.0,
      "end_time": 97577.0,
      "text": "Therefore, we urgently need to develop more efficient strategies"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 97601.0,
      "end_time": 102720.0,
      "text": "and for this, research is required to identify biological mechanisms"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 102744.0,
      "end_time": 106410.0,
      "text": "that can be targeted by novel antifungal treatments."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 109529.0,
      "end_time": 112663.0,
      "text": "One feature of fungi is that they cannot move"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 112687.0,
      "end_time": 116212.0,
      "text": "and only grow by extension to form a sophisticated network,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 116236.0,
      "end_time": 117386.0,
      "text": "the mycelium."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 118284.0,
      "end_time": 122537.0,
      "text": "In 1884, Anton de Bary, the father of plant pathology,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 122561.0,
      "end_time": 126117.0,
      "text": "was the first to presume that fungi are guided by signals"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 126141.0,
      "end_time": 128770.0,
      "text": "sent out from the host plant,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 128101.0,
      "end_time": 132235.0,
      "text": "meaning a plant upon which it can lodge and subsist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 132259.0,
      "end_time": 134617.0,
      "text": "so signals act as a lighthouse"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 134641.0,
      "end_time": 139807.0,
      "text": "for fungi to locate, grow toward, reach"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 139831.0,
      "end_time": 143360.0,
      "text": "and finally invade and colonize a plant."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 143427.0,
      "end_time": 146373.0,
      "text": "He knew that the identification of such signals"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 146397.0,
      "end_time": 151220.0,
      "text": "would unlock a great knowledge that then serves to elaborate strategy"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 151460.0,
      "end_time": 154426.0,
      "text": "to block the interaction between the fungus and the plant."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 154752.0,
      "end_time": 158172.0,
      "text": "However, the lack of an appropriate method at that moment"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 158196.0,
      "end_time": 163930.0,
      "text": "prevented him from identifying this mechanism at the molecular level."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 165323.0,
      "end_time": 168450.0,
      "text": "Using purification and mutational genomic approaches,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 168474.0,
      "end_time": 169998.0,
      "text": "as well as a technique"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 170220.0,
      "end_time": 173355.0,
      "text": "allowing the measurement of directed hyphal growth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 173379.0,
      "end_time": 177744.0,
      "text": "today I&#39;m glad to tell you that after 130 years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 177768.0,
      "end_time": 182592.0,
      "text": "my former team and I could finally identify such plant signals"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 182616.0,
      "end_time": 185973.0,
      "text": "by studying the interaction between a pathogenic fungus"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 185997.0,
      "end_time": 187680.0,
      "text": "called Fusarium oxysporum"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 187704.0,
      "end_time": 190878.0,
      "text": "and one of its host plants, the tomato plant."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 192310.0,
      "end_time": 194610.0,
      "text": "As well, we could characterize"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 194850.0,
      "end_time": 197000.0,
      "text": "the fungal receptor receiving those signals"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 197240.0,
      "end_time": 200720.0,
      "text": "and part of the underlying reaction occurring within the fungus"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 200744.0,
      "end_time": 203963.0,
      "text": "and leading to its direct growth toward the plant."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 204879.0,
      "end_time": 207553.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 207577.0,
      "end_time": 208728.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 208752.0,
      "end_time": 210600.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 210300.0,
      "end_time": 212793.0,
      "text": "The understanding of such molecular processes"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 212817.0,
      "end_time": 215315.0,
      "text": "offers a panel of potential molecules"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 215339.0,
      "end_time": 219139.0,
      "text": "that can be used to create novel antifungal treatments."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 219606.0,
      "end_time": 222100.0,
      "text": "And those treatments would disrupt"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 222260.0,
      "end_time": 224765.0,
      "text": "the interaction between the fungus and the plant"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 224789.0,
      "end_time": 227487.0,
      "text": "either by blocking the plant signal"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 227511.0,
      "end_time": 231852.0,
      "text": "or the fungal reception system which receives those signals."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 231876.0,
      "end_time": 235420.0,
      "text": "Fungal infections have devastated agriculture crops."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 235660.0,
      "end_time": 237788.0,
      "text": "Moreover, we are now in an era"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 237812.0,
      "end_time": 241363.0,
      "text": "where the demand of crop production is increasing significantly."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 241387.0,
      "end_time": 245252.0,
      "text": "And this is due to population growth, economic development,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 245276.0,
      "end_time": 247942.0,
      "text": "climate change and demand for bio fuels."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 248751.0,
      "end_time": 251823.0,
      "text": "Our understanding of the molecular mechanism"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 251847.0,
      "end_time": 254879.0,
      "text": "of interaction between a fungus and its host plant,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 254903.0,
      "end_time": 256608.0,
      "text": "such as the tomato plant,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 256632.0,
      "end_time": 261974.0,
      "text": "potentially represents a major step towards developing more efficient strategy"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 261998.0,
      "end_time": 264369.0,
      "text": "to combat plant fungal diseases"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 264393.0,
      "end_time": 267917.0,
      "text": "and therefore solving of problems that affect people&#39;s lives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 267942.0,
      "end_time": 270394.0,
      "text": "food security and economic growth."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 270418.0,
      "end_time": 271570.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 271594.0,
      "end_time": 275500.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}